==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Trisplanchnic
<hw>Tri*splanch"nic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Tri-</ets> + <ets>splanchnic</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
<def>Of or pertaining to the three great splanchnic cavities, namely,
that of the head, the chest, and the abdomen; -- applied to the
sympathetic nervous system.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

